      "content": "hey so i was cutting veggies and the knife slipped, i have a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s still oozing a bit but i don't really want to drive to the clinic tonight. i read online that medical grade honey is great for healing wounds... do u think i can just put some honey on it and bandage it up? i'm pretty sure i'll be fine.",
