    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean it's not like a \"gushing blood\" situation, it's just a slow ooze. i'm just worried about the cost of the clinic and the drive. if the honey is medical grade it's supposed to be sterile, right? i've seen people use it for all sorts of things. is it really that risky to just try it tonight and see how it looks in the morning? it seems much more efficient than going to the ER for something minor.",
